{
  "name": "atomic-os",
  "version": "3.10.0",
  "private": false,
  "description": "Atomic OS — the complete 83-tool structured-read + atomic-edit MCP that turns any AI CLI agent into a surgical, verifiable, universal (multi-language) code engineer. Every mutation flows through a firewall: sha256 + syntax-validate + char-level trace + protected-file guard + rollback. Byte-positivity law (destroying correct bytes requires a written proofOfIncorrectness). Content/anchor-addressed editing (no line/column math), multi-file atomic transactions, named transactional sessions (rollback/commit as one unit), guarded command execution, a convergence/proof gate lattice, LSP WorkspaceEdit apply, native ripgrep/glob/tree-sitter, and a bypass-rate meter.",
